text.tspan: Stuart is a bird that, due to experiments done on him
by Anastasia, has the intelligence level and cognitive
ability of a four-year-old child. As a result, he has
become amazing friends with Abby, and they enjoy
playing pranks on anyone and everyone. It’s light-
hearted, but after a while it gets really fucking
annoying. Stuart, being a raven, hates scarecrows.
Because of this, he and Barry don’t get along very
well. Stuart really likes to fly. Unfortunately, he is
unable to, because he was never taught how to by his
parents, since he never really knew them. He is
determined to fly, however, and will just jump off of
high ledges. This would kill your average flightless
bird, but whatever Anastasia did to him, it made him
pretty much invincible, as far as we know. So he falls
a lot.
Stuart
The Bird
Age: 3
Species: Raven
Alignment: Good
Stuart doesn't like
Barry that much
